messages.content:
Turning on the {room} lights

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOnLight",
  "entities": {
    "group": "all",
    "device": "lights"
  }
}
</action>

The all is now on.

I'll help you with that activatescene request.

<action>
{
  "intent": "ActivateScene",
  "entities": {
    "routine": "good night"
  }
}
</action>

Unlocking the door

<action>
{
  "intent": "UnlockDoor",
  "entities": {
    "door": "door"
  }
}
</action>

The door has been unlocked.

Turning on the living room {device}

<action>
{
  "intent": "TurnOnLight",
  "entities": {
    "room": "living room"
  }
}
</action>

The living room is now on.

I've locked the front door

<action>
{
  "intent": "LockDoor",
  "entities": {
    "door": "front door"
  }
}
</action>

The door has been locked.
